         <div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/><w lemma="κοιμάω">Ἐ<lb n="2" break="no"/>κοιμή<lb n="3" break="no"/>θη</w> <w lemma="ὁ">ἱ</w> <w lemma="δοῦλος">δούλοι</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w>
               <lb n="4"/><persName type="divine" key="theos"><roleName><w lemma="θεός"><expan><abbr>θ</abbr><ex>εο</ex><abbr>ῦ</abbr></expan></w></roleName></persName>
               <persName type="attested" ref="#person163"><name nymRef="Χαδσυμινια" cert="low">Χα<unclear>δ</unclear>συμ<lb n="5" break="no"/>ινια</name></persName>, <w lemma="υἱός">υἱὸς</w> <surplus><orig>Τ
               <lb n="6"/>Σ</orig></surplus> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w>
               <persName type="attested" ref="#person164"><name nymRef="Ἰωαννίκιος">Ἰ<unclear>ω</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ανικ</supplied><lb n="7" break="no"/>έου</name></persName>, <w lemma="ἐπί">ἐπὶ</w>
               <w lemma="ἔτος"><expan><abbr>ἔ<supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied></abbr><ex>ους</ex></expan></w> 
               <num value="6870">ς<lb n="8" break="no"/>ωο</num> .
               <w lemma="ἰνδικτιών"><expan><abbr>ἰ<unclear>ν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">δ</supplied></abbr><supplied reason="lost"><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></supplied></expan></w>
               <supplied reason="lost"><num value="15">ιε</num></supplied>.
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="ru">
            <p>Почила раба Божья Хадсиминия (?), дочь Ио<supplied reason="lost">анник</supplied>ия, в <supplied reason="lost">6</supplied>870 году, в <supplied reason="lost">15-й</supplied> ин<supplied reason="lost">дикт</supplied>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Fell asleep: a servant of God, Chadsyminia (?), daughter of Io[annik]ios, in the year <supplied reason="lost">6</supplied>870, in the <supplied reason="lost">15th</supplied> in<supplied reason="lost">diction</supplied>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="ru">
            <p> 1–4. Относительно формулы см. <ref type="introduction">IV.3.F.e</ref>.  </p>
                <!--<p> 4–5. Об имени Хадсиминия (?) см. прил. 2. </p>-->
            <p> 5. Υἱὸς для обозначения дочери встречается также в <ref type="inscription">V 140</ref><!--byz135--> из Лак (1421 г.).  </p>
            <p> 6–7. Имя Иоанникий известно в Северном Причерноморье по таманской надписи <ref type="inscription">V 340</ref><!--byz316--> 
                    (1078 г.), правда, как монашеское.</p>
                <p>7–8. Датировочная формула ἐπὶ ἔτους характерна именно для надписей из Керменчика 
                    (см. подр. <ref type="introduction">III.1.C.b</ref>). Напротив, упоминание индикта уникально для керменчикских надписей.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
            <p>1-4. On the formula, see Introduction <ref type="introduction">IV.3.F.e</ref>.</p>
            <!--<p>4-5. On the name Khadsyminia (?), see Appendix 2.</p>-->
            <p>5. Υἱὸς in reference to a daughter is also attested in <ref type="inscription">V 140</ref><!--byz135--> from Laki (1421 C.E.)</p>
            <p>6-7. The name Ioannikios (here Ioanikeos) is known in the Northern Black Sea region in one inscription from Taman - <ref type="inscription">V 340</ref><!--byz316--> 
            (1078 C.E.), although is it a monk's name in that case.</p>
            <p>7-8. The dating formula ἐπὶ ἔτους is typical for inscriptions from Kermenchik (for more detail, see Introduction <ref type="introduction">III.1.C.b</ref>),
               while a reference to indiction is otherwise unknown in this location. 
            </p>
         </div>
